<title>
Reduction Drive Gear Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306003">Transfer Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306004">Transfer Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306005">Transfer Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306006001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
Remove bearings (1) from reduction drive gear (2) using special tool, bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press (4).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C008">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85230">
09913–85230
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330018.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.566mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "135"/>
</figure>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306006002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clean all components thoroughly, inspect them for any abnormality and replace with new one as necessary.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install bearings (1) to reduction drive gear (2) using special tool, bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press (4).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C009">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85230">
09913–85230
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330019.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.650mm" ver = "01" gw = "158" gh = "136"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
